title: why riot?
body: I wanna ask why the listing of champs is different for the pregame lobby and the post game lobby, i thought maybe it had something to do with changing  in game using tab but i never do that however the listing always changes

replies.body: problem with that is I dont play ranked, only normals
It is because of the dynamic queue system, something I noticed immediately on launch but didn't care. I rearrange the TAB board into top/jug/mid/adc/sup every game anyway.
